ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

This repository demonstrates the basic usage of Docker Compose to run multiple containers together using official Docker images.

The setup uses:

Python container

MySQL container

Docker Compose to orchestrate both

This project is created for learning, practice, and interview preparation, especially on Amazon EC2 (Amazon Linux).
