=========================================================

ğŸ§  Key Concepts Learned

Docker Compose manages multiple containers

Uses service names instead of IP addresses

Automatically creates a default Docker network

One YAML file controls the entire application

âš ï¸ Common Issues & Fixes
âŒ dockercompose: command not found

âœ” Use:

