âŒ no configuration file provided

âœ” File name must be:

docker-compose.yml

âŒ Permission denied

âœ” Fix:

sudo chmod +x /usr/local/bin/docker-compose

ğŸ”„ Useful Commands
docker-compose up        # Start services
docker-compose up -d     # Start in background
docker-compose down      # Stop & clean
docker ps                # List running containers

â­ Interview Question

Q: What is Docker Compose used for?
A: Docker Compose is used to define and run multi-container Docker applications using a single YAML file.

